{{Youmay|a real-world author and illustrator|[[Alex (disambiguation)|other uses of the term Alex]]}}
'''Alex Jaeger''' is an employee of [[Industrial Light & Magic]] who was a visual effects layout and storyboard artist for the [[The Star Wars Trilogy Special Edition|Special Edition]] of {{Film|VI}},<ref name="VI">{{Film|VI}}</ref> visual effects art director for {{Film|II}},<ref name="II">{{Film|II}}</ref> and visual effects concept artist for {{Film|VII}}.<ref name="VII">{{Film|VII}}</ref> Jaeger was also the visual effects art director for the ''[[Star Wars: Squadrons]]'' short "[[Hunted]],"<ref name="Hunted">{{EASWYouTube|f2VmOqjV_7Q|"Hunted"|int=Hunted}}</ref> and wrote and illustrated the ''[[Star Wars: Visionaries]]'' comic "[[Entrenched]]" with [[M. Zachary Sherman]].<ref name="Entrenched">{{StoryCite|story=Entrenched|book=Star Wars: Visionaries}}</ref>

